values.comment:
Construct a result from model and cmd, flipped for piping:

   { model | foo = bar }
     |> withCmd someCmd

Construct a result from model without cmd, flipped for piping:

   { model | foo = bar }
     |> withNone

Construct a result from model and task, flipped for piping:

   { model | foo = bar }
     |> withTask someTask
